doing likely to make it

00:53:57.530 --> 00:54:00.280
such that next year and the
year after that, and five

00:54:00.280 --> 00:54:02.090
years from that, and
10 years after that,

00:54:02.090 --> 00:54:05.640
they'd be more likely to be
making new highs than new lows.

00:54:05.640 --> 00:54:08.110
It's a very gross
distinction, but I

00:54:08.110 --> 00:54:11.325
